snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Year 2 Character Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Behold, the Year 2 roster for Street Fighter 6!

M. Bison - Summer 2024
Terry - Autumn 2024
Mai - Winter 2025
Elena - Spring 2025

From Fatal Fury by SNK, the first two guest characters to ever grace the Street Fighter series are joined by two high-spirited veterans.
